<emphasis id="B9078C2AFFF3FF92FE019351FDA1F7F8" bold="true" box="[394,588,2137,2170]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="62">Diagnose</emphasis>
. — Vert-bronzé. Une tache devant chaque oeil 
<emphasis id="B9078C2AFFF3FF92FA289351FA00F7F8" box="[1443,1517,2137,2170]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="62">et la</emphasis>
