<emphasis id="B9078C2AFFF3FF92F9049351F941F7F8" box="[1679,1708,2137,2170]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="62">la</emphasis>
lèvre supérieure jaunes. 
<emphasis id="B9078C2AFFF3FF92FD4A9398FD06F733" box="[705,747,2192,2225]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="62">La</emphasis>
plupart 
<emphasis id="B9078C2AFFF3FF92FC1B9398FC2BF733" bold="true" box="[912,966,2192,2225]" pageId="6" pageNumber="62">des</emphasis>
segments de l'abdomen avec 
<emphasis id="B9078C2AFFF3FF92FA5C9398F9E1F733" bold="true" box="[1495,1548,2192,2225]" pageId="6" pageNumber="62">des</emphasis>
taches margi­ nales jaunes. 
<emphasis id="B9078C2AFFF3FF92FE01921FFD90F6BA" bold="true" box="[394,637,2327,2360]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="62">Dimensions</emphasis>
. — (Voyez le
</paragraph>
